<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
    <diagram id="SequenceDiagramUploaddra" name="Sequence Diagram - Upload">
        <mxGraphModel dx="1400" dy="900" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
            <root>
                <mxCell id="0"/>
                <mxCell id="1" parent="0"/>
                <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&quot;data&quot;: &quot;\nsequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n\n    actor User as Người dùng (guest hoặc đã đăng nhập)\n    participant FE as Frontend (React SPA)\n    participant API as Backend API /api/v1\n    participant TH as core.rate_limit (bảng ai_throttle)\n    participant Scan as ScanService\n    participant Store as Object Storage\n    participant Pipe as ScanPipeline (background task)\n    participant OCR as Google Vision (OCR)\n    participant LLM as Gemini (parser + translation)\n    participant DB as PostgreSQL\n\n    rect rgb(239, 246, 255)\n        User-&gt;&gt;FE: Chọn ảnh/PDF menu + ngôn ngữ đích\n        FE-&gt;&gt;FE: Validate: mỗi file ≤ 10MB, tổng ≤ 40MB, ≤ 8 trang\n        FE-&gt;&gt;API: POST /api/v1/scans (multipart/form-data)\n        Note over API: Auth KHÔNG bắt buộc&lt;br/&gt;(get_optional_current_user)\n    end\n\n    rect rgb(254, 249, 195)\n        API-&gt;&gt;TH: enforce_scan_throttle(user hoặc IP)\n        TH-&gt;&gt;DB: upsert atomic vào ai_throttle\n        DB--&gt;&gt;TH: OK (đủ khoảng cách tối thiểu)\n        TH--&gt;&gt;API: cho phép\n    end\n\n    rect rgb(248, 250, 252)\n        API-&gt;&gt;Scan: create_scan(files, target_language, user?)\n        Scan-&gt;&gt;Store: lưu file gốc (private)\n        Store--&gt;&gt;Scan: object_key\n        Scan-&gt;&gt;DB: INSERT scan_sessions (PENDING) + scan_source_files\n        DB--&gt;&gt;Scan: scan_id\n        Scan--&gt;&gt;API: scan_id\n        API--&gt;&gt;FE: 202 Accepted { scan_id, status: PENDING }\n        Note over API,Pipe: Trả 202 NGAY,&lt;br/&gt;xử lý chạy nền\n    end\n\n    API-&gt;&gt;Pipe: BackgroundTask: process(scan_id)\n\n    rect rgb(220, 252, 231)\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;DB: UPDATE status=PROCESSING, stage=OCR\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;Store: đọc file gốc\n        Store--&gt;&gt;Pipe: bytes\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;OCR: nhận dạng văn bản\n        OCR--&gt;&gt;Pipe: OcrDocument (text, detected_language)\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;DB: INSERT ocr_results\n\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;DB: stage=ANALYZING\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;LLM: phân tích menu → danh sách món\n        LLM--&gt;&gt;Pipe: ParsedMenuDraft (tên, mô tả, giá, nhóm)\n\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;DB: stage=TRANSLATING\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;LLM: dịch tên/mô tả sang ngôn ngữ đích\n        LLM--&gt;&gt;Pipe: draft đã dịch\n\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;DB: stage=FINALIZING\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;DB: INSERT menus + food_items\n        Pipe-&gt;&gt;DB: UPDATE status=COMPLETED\n    end\n\n    rect rgb(243, 232, 255)\n        loop Poll cho tới khi COMPLETED hoặc FAILED\n            FE-&gt;&gt;API: GET /api/v1/scans/{scan_id}\n            API--&gt;&gt;FE: { status, stage, progress }\n        end\n        FE-&gt;&gt;API: GET /api/v1/scans/{scan_id}/result\n        API--&gt;&gt;FE: menu + danh sách món\n        FE-&gt;&gt;API: GET /api/v1/scans/{scan_id}/source\n        API--&gt;&gt;FE: 302 → signed URL (file gốc, sống ngắn)\n        FE--&gt;&gt;User: Hiển thị file gốc cạnh danh sách món\n    end\n\n    Note over Pipe,LLM: Parser LLM có chuỗi dự phòng theo model,&lt;br/&gt;rồi mới về parser theo luật — một model hết quota&lt;br/&gt;không làm hỏng toàn bộ kết quả.\n&quot;}" id="2">
                    <mxCell style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;imageAspect=1;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                        <mxGeometry x="20" y="20" width="1600.0" height="1314.9" as="geometry"/>
                    </mxCell>
                </UserObject>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
    </diagram>
</mxfile>
